{"tid":1093177,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月新番]鬼滅之刃 鬼滅の刃 集中討論","createTime":"2019-04-05T11:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T17:46:25.000Z","uid":3020,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40ed30ed7cbc0eae3e3313c2e1d885d4d052f166","tid":1093177,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50aePjk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50aePjk.jpg&h=121e58ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舞台是日本的大正時代，名叫竈門炭治郎的平凡農村少年，靠著賣炭來維持一家的生計。某天他下山去賣炭，回家時天色已暗，好心的三郎爺爺變留他住了一晚。隔天他回到家卻發現家人全都遭到殘殺，只剩禰豆子身體還有餘溫，然而她似乎變得跟平常不太一樣？為了尋求拯救妹妹的方法，炭治郎踏上了斬鬼的冒險旅程。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF <br />\n原作：吾峠呼世晴<br />\n監督：外崎春雄<br />\n角色設計：松島晃<br />\n腳本制作：ufotable<br />\n音樂：梶浦由記、椎名豪<br />\n動畫制作：ufotable<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n竈門炭治郎：花江夏樹<br />\n竈門襧豆子：鬼頭明里<br />\n我妻善逸：下野紘<br />\n嘴平伊之助：松岡禎丞<br />\n冨岡義勇：櫻井孝宏<br />\n鱗滝左近次：大塚芳忠 <br />\n錆兎：梶裕貴<br />\n真菰：加隈亜衣 <br />\n玄弥：岡本信彦<br />\n産屋敷耀哉：森川智之<br />\n案内役・白髪：井澤詩織 <br />\n案内役・黒髪：悠木碧 <br />\n鋼鐡塚：浪川大輔 <br />\n鎹鴉：山﨑たくみ <br />\nお堂の鬼：緑川光 <br />\n手鬼：子安武人<br />\n官方網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://kimetsu.com/anime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkimetsu.com%2Fanime%2F&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=b9957cf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://kimetsu.com/anime/</a><br />\n4月6日 22:30<br />\n<a href=\"https://mov3.co/en/tokyomx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmov3.co%2Fen%2Ftokyomx%2F&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=f310b35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://mov3.co/en/tokyomx/</a><br />\n4月7日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/media/md22718131/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fbangumi%2Fmedia%2Fmd22718131%2F&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=5665c8ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/media/md22718131/</a><br />\n漫畫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dm5.com/manhua